Title: ERSrcEtOH01hr_rna
Extraction_Protocol: For RNA-seq, total RNA was purified from DNase-treated lysates, and ribosomal RNA was depleted with RiboMinus Eukaryote Kit (Invitrogen). RNA-seq libraries were prepared with a tagging-based workflow(Pease and Kinross, 2013). In brief, rRNA-depleted RNA was fragmented at 85°C for 5 min, followed by cDNA synthesis, terminal tagging and PCR amplification with ScriptSeq v2 RNA-Seq Library Preparation Kit (Epicentre).

Title: ERSrcTAM00hr_chx_rep1
Extraction_Protocol: For ribosome profiling, cells were pretreated with cycloheximide (100 µg/ml; Sigma-Aldrich) for 90 seconds or harringtonine (2 µg/ml; Santa Cruz) for 5 minutes, and detergent lysis was then performed with flash-freezing in liquid nitrogen. DNase I-treated lysates were then treated with RNase I, and ribosome-protected fragments were purified as previously described (Ingolia et al., 2012). For ribosome profiling, ribosome-protected fragments were subjected to Illumina TruSeq library construction as previously described (Ingolia et al., 2012).
